{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, I had put the ones with the drop container on top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, into the reach of the fan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And within about one second I had ruined 2,000 of these items.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Needless to say, I was not kept in that position.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was transferred to something else, but became sort of a very funny famous figure [? in the house. ?] Well, that-- it was very, very hard work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And pretty soon, I thought that's no use.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I better return to Dresden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I returned to Dresden and was immediately imprisoned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My girlfriend, the daughter of the director of the Kulturbund, was partly Gentile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Her mother was Gentile, and she had the privilege of all Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one of the-- the cook went to the Gestapo and said, look what she's doing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She has all the privileges, but the only think he can think of is a Jewish boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we both were put into prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She in Berlin and I in Dresden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE], the big factory for optical instruments, employed all the Jews in Dresden, and they had heard about me as a young person.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was immediately claimed by them, and I got out of camp-- I got out of prison.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And worked at [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Neither my father nor my mother worked there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They had other duties, and there came the first big wave of deportation as part of the final solution.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my parents were deported, and my brother and myself were left behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So our plan to be with our parents was moot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Riga.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She transferred to Riga.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother died in Riga of a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
